    {
        "source_sentence": "彼於夢境執以為實，是智者不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b20_25",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王言：「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b21_26",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b21_27",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b21_28",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夢中畢竟無彼幻師，況復變現五欲等事。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b22_29",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人徒自疲勞，都無有實。」",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，如是！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚癡寡聞凡夫異生意著於法，心生貪染，復起追求，轉增癡愛，為彼所牽，造如是罪，身業三種、語業四種、意業三種，造作彼業，剎那遷謝。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼業滅已，不依東方南西北方四維上下中間而住，至命終時，見昔所作心想中現，自分業報皆悉現前，猶如夢覺念夢中事。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c01_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "識為其主，業為攀緣，二種相因，初識生起，作業受報，皆不失壞，或趣地獄，或墮傍生、琰摩羅界及阿脩羅，若人若天。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初識生已各受其報，同分心品相續隨轉，最後識滅名為死蘊，最初識起名為生蘊。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身識生時，無所從來，滅無所至；彼緣生時，無所從來，滅無所至；彼業生時，無所從來，滅無所至。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c05_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c07_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無有少法從於此世得至他世。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自性空故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是了知初識初識空，自業自業空，身識身識空，若滅滅空，若生生空，輪迴輪迴空，涅槃涅槃皆自性空。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作業不可得，受報不可得，但唯名相分別顯示。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知諸根如幻境界如夢，一切諸法皆悉空寂，此名空解脫門；空無空相，名無相解脫門；若無相者則無希求，名無願解脫門。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依此了知三解脫門，與空共行，菩提先道，廣大如法界，究竟如虛空。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於此譬喻，當如是知。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如有人於睡夢中，為彼瀑流漂沒己身及其眷屬，受諸惶怖種種苦惱。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人覺已，憶念夢中水所漂溺，為實爾不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王言：「不也！」",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人所夢執以為實，是智者不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王言：「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c21_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c21_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夢中畢竟無水所漂，況復有彼惶怖苦惱？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c22_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人徒自疲勞，都無有實。」",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，如是！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚癡寡聞凡夫異生，意著諸法生憂惱處，展轉尋求無對治道，以不了故起諸惡行，身業三種、語業四種、意業三種，造作彼業，剎那遷謝。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是業滅已，不依東方南西北方四維上下中間而住，至命終時心生惶怖，見昔所作悉現其前，如人夢覺念夢中事。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "識為其主，業為攀緣，二種相因，初識生起，作業受果皆不失壞，或趣地獄，或墮傍生、琰摩羅界及阿脩羅，若人若天。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970c29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初識生已，各受其報，同分心品相續不絕，最後識滅名為死蘊，最初識起名為生蘊。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971a03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971a05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初識生時，無所從來，滅無所至；彼緣生時，無所從來，滅無所至；彼業生時，無所從來，滅無所至。",
