        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971a15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於此譬喻，當如是知。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971a16_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971a18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如有人於睡夢中，自見其身飲酒惛醉，不識善法及諸惡行，功德過失都不覺知。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971a18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人覺已，念夢中事，為實爾不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971a20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王言：「不也！」",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971a20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971a21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971a21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人所夢執為真實，是智者不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971a21_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王言：「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971a22_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
