        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971a22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971a22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夢中畢竟無飲酒者，況惛醉耶？",
